        <h7>Daily General Fund Revenues Vs. Expenditures</h7>
        <p>This chart compares actual General Fund revenues and expenditures by day.</p>
        <p>All information based on transactions processed by the Treasury Department. Current fiscal year totals are as of last business day.</p>
        <hr>
        <h7>Historical Fund Cash Balances</h7>
        <p>This chart lists the selected funds total asset balance at cost value. This is the balance Treasury utilizes as an expendable fund balance. The balance reflected is the asset balance as of that day and does not include outstanding bills that need to be paid, planned spending that will occur later in the fiscal year, or planned spending that will occur in future fiscal years.</p>
        <p>All information based on transactions processed by the Treasury Department. Current fiscal year totals are as of last business day.</p>
        <hr>
        <h7>Fiscal Year Revenues Vs. Expenditures</h7>
